OL,3,CBrave officers honoured for their 'the
OL,4,Cultimate sacrifice' to policing
OL,6,FTwo brave officers who died in the
OL,7,Fline of duty will be honoured for
OL,8,Frisking their lives to protect the
OL,9,Fpublic.
OL,11,FThe Government announced the
OL,12,Fintroduction of The Elizabeth Emblem
OL,13,Fin March this year.
OL,15,FThis commemorative emblem is awarded
OL,16,Fas a mark of recognition to the next
OL,17,Fof kin of those who lost their lives
OL,18,Fduring public service.
