OL,3,CBrave officers honoured for their 'the
OL,4,Cultimate sacrifice' to policing
OL,6,FPC Christopher McDonald and PC Ged
OL,7,FWalker have been recognised and their
OL,8,Ffamilies will receive the award in
OL,9,Fhonour of their bravery, courage, and
OL,10,Fdedication.
OL,12,FPC McDonald was only 19-years-old when
OL,13,Fhe was killed on 17 May 1978, after
OL,14,Fcoming across a break-in at a
OL,15,Fjewellers' shop in Worksop. He bravely
OL,16,Fconfronting a gang of offenders before
OL,17,Fchasing them.
OL,19,FIn a subsequent struggle with a
OL,20,Fsuspect, the young officer suffered
OL,21,Fserious head injuries.
