OL,6,FHis mum will receive the Elizabeth
OL,7,FEmblem in his honour.
OL,9,FHis sisters Elaine Dean and Carol
OL,10,FBullock said: "As a family we are
OL,11,Freally pleased to receive the Emblem.
OL,13,F"It is really good that he is going to
OL,14,Fbe remembered all these years on. It
OL,15,Fhas been a long time coming.
OL,17,F"I don't think a lot of people realise
OL,18,Fthat officers put their lives in
OL,19,Fdanger every day when they go to work.
