OL,6,F"There are not many jobs where people
OL,7,Fare faced with these situations. They
OL,8,Fare the thin blue line, and we are
OL,9,Freally proud as a family."
OL,11,FDog handler PC Ged Walker died 21
OL,12,Fyears ago. He was on duty in Bulwell
OL,13,Fwhen he was fatally injured as he
OL,14,Ftried to stop a stolen taxi. He died
OL,15,Fof his injuries two days later on 9
OL,16,FJanuary 2003.
OL,18,FHis wife Tracy will receive the
OL,19,FElizabeth Emblem in his honour.
