OL,6,FShe said: "We are very proud, and it
OL,7,Fis nice for the police to be
OL,8,Facknowledged by the government for
OL,9,Fwhat he did. I think police officers
OL,10,Fshould be recognised.
OL,12,F"He has lost his life serving the
OL,13,Fcommunity. There is no greater
OL,14,Fsacrifice and something that was never
OL,15,Fexpected. You never imagine someone
OL,16,Fgoing to work at 6am and getting a
OL,17,Fcall at 3pm saying this has happened
OL,18,Fto them."
