OL,4,Cultimate sacrifice' to policing
OL,6,FChief Constable Kate Meynell said she
OL,7,Fis pleased both officers continue to
OL,8,Fbe recognised for their bravery and
OL,9,Fcourage.
OL,11,FShe said: "They made the ultimate
OL,12,Fsacrifice in their heroic attempts to
OL,13,Fuphold the law and protect the
OL,14,Fcommunity from harm.
OL,16,F"Their loss is still felt across the
OL,17,Fforce to this day and their service
OL,18,Fand sacrifice will never be forgotten."
